'''Tree''' is an unused scenery object that may have been intended for use in [[Rooftop Agility Courses]]. The tree has the same interaction options and examine text as the [[Tree (Pollnivneach Rooftop Course)|tree]] in the [[Pollnivneach Rooftop Course]], but has slightly different dimensions. Similar to other agility obstacles, the tree object does not have a visible model, and would instead have been used as a region near the tree that would be clicked to jump over the obstacle.
